   YOUR DIGITAL
   ACCESS INCLUDES
     * Unlimited online access
     * HEALTH Digital Magazine
     * Healthy & delicious recipes, energizing workouts, and the latest
       beauty trends from the editors

   Click on the icons below for instructions on how to access the digital
   edition of HEALTH.

   DIGITAL EDITION AVAILABLE ON
   [1]App Store
   App StoreOptimized for iPad® and iPhone®
